+```
+
+Production build:
+
+```bash
+npm run build -w react-native-web-docs
+```
+
+Debug mode:
+
+```bash
+npm run debug -w react-native-web-docs
+```
+
+## TV docs in this fork
+
+This fork includes TV-focused docs pages covering:
+
+* TV navigation and focus model
+* `TVFocusGuideView`
+* `TVEventHandler`
+* `TVEventControl`
+* `useTVEventHandler`
